<section class="porfolio-highlight">
  <h2>GreenCrate</h2>
  <div class="sub-head">
    Delivering the greenhouse to your doorstep.
  </div>
  <div class="overline">Overview</div>
  <p>
    GreenCrate is a California based startup formed in 2020 aiming to bring
    organic produce, at affordable prices, directly from the greenhouse to your
    doorstep. As lead product designer, I designed GreenCrate’s core user flows
    and defined the visual language for the team, and defined a user testing
    plan and supporting designs for a series of video based greenhouse tours and
    virtual farmers market experiences the team was experimenting with. The
    Android and iOS application are currently under development.
  </p>
