<section class="porfolio-highlight">
  <h2>BillGuru</h2>
  <div class="sub-head">
    Making savings & budgeting simple.
  </div>
  <div class="overline">Overview</div>
  <p>
    BillGuru brings clarity to the stressful and confusing process of figuring
    out how to pay your bills when you don't have enough money to cover all of
    them. The product enables users to organize and track their bills, and
    calculates which ones are most important to pay with the money they have
    available. As product designer on the team, I led visual design and defined
    core flows across the product. Born at a Hackathon in San Francisco, the
    idea won grand prize, earning it a spot as one of ten finalist teams in the
    national FinCapDev Competition. The app is no longer active.
  </p>
</section>

